    dc:creator "Albertoni, Fabiano F." ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Morphology and natural history of two species of bromeliad leaf beetles in the genus Calliaspis Dejean, 1836 from Southern Brazil, with a summary of the current knowledge of Imatidiini immatures (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Cassidinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.852116> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.852116>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 25. Calliaspis umbonata Hincks, 1956 mature larva. (16) Clypeus and labrum; (17) epipharynx; (18, 19) lateral outlines of labrum and epipharynx in frontal view; (20) scale-like projections of epipharynx; (21) maxilla and labium, ventral view; (22) maxilla and hypopharynx, dorsal view; (23, 24, 25) mandible: (23) dorso-external view; (24) ventro-internal view; (25) external view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/852116/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

